					<h4>Privacy Policy for Meal Picker</h4>
					<p>Effective Date: December 2021</p>
					<p>This policy outlines how we treat your personal information. Various portions of the site collect personal information, this policy outlines what we do with it and how information is collected.</p>
					<h4>How information is collected:</h4>
					<p>Directly from you: When placing an order</p>
					<p>Third Parties: Sites that we advertise with may share information about you. Social media sites for example. Other business partners may also share information.</p>
					<h4>What information is collected:</h4>
					<p>Contact Information: Your name and email address may be collected if you volunteer it. Your address, phone number, Meal Picker, etc may also be collected.</p>
					<h4>Usage and Device information:</h4>
					<p>When visiting this website, information about your browser type, operating system, IP address, and the domain from which you came are collected. Except for what you submit to us, we do not collect any personally identifiable information. Any personally identifiable information that you give us will only be used to respond to you and will not be retained. Any information that we do collect is only used in aggregate to determine whether improvements can be made in our service. The information is not permanently stored. Any information that we collect is stored using a cookie that is placed on your computer. We do NOT use this cookie to collect or store personally identifiable information about you. However, the cookie is used to track information about how you interact with our website. It also allows our website to be customized to meet your interests.</p>
					<h4>How we use your information:</h4>
					<p>To respond to requests and produce quotes: Your location, for example, is needed for an accurate shipping estimate. Other information may be used depending on the request you have made.</p>
					<p>For security purposes: Your information may be used to protect Meal Pick and our customers. Your information may also be used to protect our sites.</p>
					<p>Marketing purposes: Your information allows us to communicate promotions, sales, and other opportunities we offer. Your information is also used when advertising to you across various platforms. This is done only when legally permitted.</p>
					<p>Processing Orders: Your information is used to ensure your order is accurate and shipped to the correct location. Other information may be used to service the order.</p>
					<h4>Who your information is shared with:</h4>
					<p>Third parties: Trusted third parties such as the company that delivers your product may require your information. Other vendors and companies that we work with may also receive your information if required.</p>
					<p>Law Enforcement: Your information will be shared with the authorities if required via court order or subpoena. Other government agencies may also receive your information upon request. This applies to U.S. and foreign government agencies.</p>
					<p>Business Partners: In order to market to you and serve you effectively, your information may be shared with other companies we do business with.</p>
					<p>Other parties: In rare cases your information may be shared with other parties as permitted by law.</p>
					<h4>Your options:</h4>
					<p>Opt outs: If you wish to no longer receive our marketing emails please get ahold of us via the chat function. Upon opt out you may still receive non-marketing emails only when necessary.</p>
					<p>Updating your information: You may update your information by contacting us through the chat function. We will also delete your information upon request.</p>
					<h4>Other information:</h4>
					<p>Our sites are not intended for children: Our websites are intended for adult use only. If you are a parent or legal guardian and concerned that your child has given us information, please contact us through the chat function.</p>
					<p>Security measures: Reasonable security measures are taken to protect your information. However, the internet is not perfectly secure. We cannot guarantee absolute safety when using our site. Please use caution and discretion when using the internet.</p>
					<p>How long we keep your information: Your information is kept for long as needed or the purposes outlined in this policy. We will delete your information at any time upon request.</p>
